ch.fhnw.ht.eit.p2.impedancepro
Class ImpedanceProController

java.lang.Object
  ch.fhnw.ht.eit.p2.impedancepro.ImpedanceProController

public class ImpedanceProController
extends java.lang.Object

The ImpedanceProController class triggers the models calculations, as soon as there are changes in the view. It also changes settings of the view.

Author:
Simon Zumbrunnen
